CEPHO.AI
Grand Master Plan — v11
Version 11.0 | March 2026 | CONFIDENTIAL
The Single Source of Truth. AI Foundations First. Automation by Design.

---

Executive Summary
CEPHO.AI is an autonomous platform designed to replicate and automate the core functions of a world-
class Chief of Staff. This Grand Master Plan is the single, definitive roadmap for transforming the
platform from its current Grade E state to Grade A+ — a genuinely intelligent, fully automated,
enterprise-ready platform.
This version restructures the phases so that AI architecture foundations are built early — in Phase 2 —
rather than bolted on at the end. The deep automation layer (autonomous task creation, anomaly
detection, natural language commands, vector knowledge base) is built in Phase 3, before the scaling
and operational work begins. This ensures every subsequent phase builds on a solid AI foundation
rather than retrofitting AI into a system that was not designed for it.

