Deployment Gate Protocol
No deployment reaches production without all 8 gates passing. Gates 1–5 are enforced automatically by
the CI/CD pipeline. Gates 6–8 require human sign-off.
Gate Check Enforced By
1 TypeScript compilation: tsc --noEmit CI/CD automatic
passes with zero errors
2 ESLint passes with zero errors CI/CD automatic
3 All unit and contract tests pass: CI/CD automatic
pnpm test
4 Build succeeds: pnpm build CI/CD automatic
5 Security scan: pnpm audit --audit- CI/CD automatic
level=critical passes
6 Validation script passes: python3 Developer manual
scripts/validate.py --check ALL
7 GRADES.md updated with new Developer manual
grade and evidence of improvement
8 CHANGELOG.md updated with Developer manual
summary of changes in this
deployment

